   </tbody>
  </table>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_set_colour(c_lime); draw_line(50,50,150,50);
</code></pre>
  This will draw a light green horizontal line from point (50,50) to point (150,50).
